groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Whip it - Whip it Good!!!
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: Picturesque if somewhat off the beatern track in horse country, there is a bridge between old country and new.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
You might want to take the time for a pint or two before you leave, but don't forget to look at the rushing river. Can be a very busy area especially on weekends, parking is catch as catch can at those times. BYOP and watch muggles. ***There is a letterbox also hidden there so please do not mistake the letterbox for the cache. The stamp is an important part of the letterbox and should not be removed. Maybe now is the time to learn more about letterboxing!!!***
Congratulations to $Hunter who was the first to find this great cache!

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Quick find after a good meal. Found with dawnie22 and 19acassel.
